allDialogue: Paracelsys? I just saw that the Mantis's life signal went out.
Hey, are these robots, ya know, sentient?
...Do you think a giant insect robot could be sentient?
But you've always said facts come first, and well...
It only attacked me because I aggravated it.
...Stop worrying over such trivial things. I'll meet you on Magus, I need to open a portal to the Gaurdian so we can defeat it.
